    **********************************
    * TNEF Attachment Decoder plugin *
    * Installation                   *
    **********************************

1. Unpack plugin in NaSMail plugins directory

   $ cd /var/www/nasmail/plugins
   $ tar -xzvf /home/archives/nasmail_plugin_attachment_tnef-0.7.nsm-1.4.tar.gz

4. Enable plugin in NaSMail configuration
    $ cd /var/www/nasmail/config
    $ ./conf.pl --install-plugin attachment_tnef

If you can't use conf.pl utility, check NaSMail documentation about other
configuration options.
